1
00:00:01,280 --> 00:00:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pretty scene.</font>

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:07,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you. All of our 
hard work has paid off.</font>

3
00:00:07,720 --> 00:00:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet everyone's delighted to live
 in such a wonderful village.</font>

4
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while since you came 
to this village. What do you think?</font>

5
00:00:16,430 --> 00:00:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

6
00:00:17,620 --> 00:00:18,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you live here?</font>

7
00:00:18,990 --> 00:00:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

8
00:00:21,370 --> 00:00:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well...</font>

9
00:00:23,460 --> 00:00:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, setting aside engagement 
proposals, what do <i>you</i> want to do?</font>

10
00:00:27,740 --> 00:00:30,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine to put your own feelings first.</font>

11
00:00:31,370 --> 00:00:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What <i>I</i> want to do?</font>

12
00:00:35,640 --> 00:00:38,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to get engaged to Lord Van.</font>

13
00:00:38,850 --> 00:00:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, um...</font>

14
00:00:40,890 --> 00:00:42,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want to get engaged?</font>

15
00:00:44,420 --> 00:00:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I pretend I didn't hear that?</font>

16
00:00:46,810 --> 00:00:48,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

17
00:00:48,020 --> 00:00:50,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. I see.</i></font>

18
00:00:50,270 --> 00:00:55,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, Lord Van, you seem 
kind of happy all of a sudden.</font>

19
00:00:55,530 --> 00:00:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're imagining it.</font>

20
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EASYGOING TERRITORY DEFENSE
BY THE OPTIMISTIC LORD</font>

21
00:01:14,550 --> 00:01:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 9: THE TIMID GIRL'S
BEAUTIFUL MARIONETTE DANCE</font>

22
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}EPISODE 9: THE TIMID GIRL'S
BEAUTIFUL MARIONETTE DANCE</font>

23
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lord Van! We've returned
 from the royal capital.</font>

24
00:02:33,250 --> 00:02:37,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back. Did you set up 
your trading company easily enough?</font>

25
00:02:37,130 --> 00:02:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. Everything went swimmingly,
thanks to you, Lord Van.</font>

26
00:02:40,890 --> 00:02:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And just as we promised, 
30 platinum. Here you are.</font>

27
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you.</font>

28
00:02:47,970 --> 00:02:50,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Till. If you would.</font>

29
00:02:53,020 --> 00:03:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}RICHES</font>

30
00:02:53,020 --> 00:02:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my first time ever handling 
such a large amount of platinum.</font>

31
00:02:56,850 --> 00:03:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, isn't Lady Panamera
coming back to the village?</font>

32
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she had to go report
 to Count Ferdinatto.</font>

33
00:03:04,290 --> 00:03:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She thinks allying with you will be more
 interesting than sticking with the count.</font>

34
00:03:09,410 --> 00:03:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? So she'll be living in this village?</font>

35
00:03:11,790 --> 00:03:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, she said her plan was to 
be given land near this village.</font>

36
00:03:15,790 --> 00:03:19,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowing Lady Panamera, I'm sure 
it won't take long for her to get it.</font>

37
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

38
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:26,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That woman's likely to become queen
 before anyone realizes.</i></font>

39
00:03:26,150 --> 00:03:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also...</font>

40
00:03:27,690 --> 00:03:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We present you with this masterpiece
 we found in the royal capital.</font>

41
00:03:32,540 --> 00:03:34,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is this what I think it is?!</font>

42
00:03:34,810 --> 00:03:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a machine bow, capable of firing
 up to ten shots in a row.</font>

43
00:03:39,490 --> 00:03:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the latest tech in the royal capital.</font>

44
00:03:42,190 --> 00:03:46,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you! I can create
 new ballistae with this!</font>

45
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:48,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yahoo!</font>

46
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I'm so happy!</font>

47
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good for you, Lord Van.</font>

48
00:03:50,450 --> 00:03:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he more excited about that
than the platinum?</font>

49
00:03:50,450 --> 00:03:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Thank you so much, you two!</font>

50
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So pulling this lever causes 
the next bolt to slide down?</font>

51
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:02,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the happiest 
I've ever seen you look, Lord Van.</font>

52
00:04:02,810 --> 00:04:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? Is it?</font>

53
00:04:09,970 --> 00:04:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible.</font>

54
00:04:11,640 --> 00:04:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? It's not moving.</font>

55
00:04:14,790 --> 00:04:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So even you fail sometimes.</font>

56
00:04:17,730 --> 00:04:19,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

57
00:04:19,110 --> 00:04:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, m-my apologies. 
I didn't mean anything by it.</font>

58
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:28,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fail at things all the time.</font>

59
00:04:28,050 --> 00:04:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aside from my magic, 
I can't pride myself in anything.</font>

60
00:04:30,790 --> 00:04:32,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not true.</font>

61
00:04:32,880 --> 00:04:36,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have amazing talent 
with the sword and with your studies.</font>

62
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:41,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really don't have anything.</font>

63
00:04:41,170 --> 00:04:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Talent?</font>

64
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:45,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd like, I'll introduce you
 to my fiendish butler</font>

65
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:48,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and the monstrous commander
 of my chivalric order.</font>

66
00:04:48,180 --> 00:04:51,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll become just as "amazing"
 as me in no time.</font>

67
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:57,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That reminds me, 
what's your magical aptitude, Arte?</font>

68
00:05:00,760 --> 00:05:03,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, Lady Arte?</font>

69
00:05:03,550 --> 00:05:06,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van won't force you to answer.</font>

70
00:05:06,500 --> 00:05:09,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you don't want to say, that's fine.</font>

71
00:05:10,050 --> 00:05:11,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

72
00:05:11,120 --> 00:05:13,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-My...</font>

73
00:05:13,750 --> 00:05:16,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My aptitude is for marionette magic.</font>

74
00:05:17,730 --> 00:05:19,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Marionette magic.</i></font>

75
00:05:19,410 --> 00:05:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just like my production magic,
it is considered useless by nobles,</i></font>

76
00:05:23,740 --> 00:05:25,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>so it is equally loathed.</i></font>

77
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However...</i></font>

78
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, I've never seen that magic before.
 Could you show it to me?</font>

79
00:05:30,890 --> 00:05:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? U-Um...</font>

80
00:05:33,870 --> 00:05:36,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-My magic?</font>

81
00:05:36,520 --> 00:05:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, people with an aptitude 
for marionette magic are rare.</font>

82
00:05:41,210 --> 00:05:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, that's probably 
because many people hide it.</font>

83
00:05:44,730 --> 00:05:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even so, you're the first person 
I've met who can use it.</font>

84
00:05:47,780 --> 00:05:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is fate, Arte.</font>

85
00:05:57,730 --> 00:06:00,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you move this?</font>

86
00:06:11,340 --> 00:06:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is incredible magic!</font>

87
00:06:13,670 --> 00:06:16,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's limitless potential 
in this magic, Arte!</font>

88
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:23,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was magnificent.
So, so impressive, Lady Arte.</font>

89
00:06:23,700 --> 00:06:28,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you also perform that dance
 you made the puppet do?</font>

90
00:06:28,190 --> 00:06:29,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, y-yes.</font>

91
00:06:29,930 --> 00:06:33,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although I'm a little better at making
the puppet dance than doing it myself.</font>

92
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, no, that's still really amazing.</font>

93
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get Lord Van to make 
more charming puppets.</font>

94
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:44,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I bet if you put on a show with them, 
the villagers would be delighted.</font>

95
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:47,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right. That does sound fun.</font>

96
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While we're at it, I can make a puppet 
using the mythril ore Arte discovered.</font>

97
00:06:52,180 --> 00:06:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But my magic isn't fit 
for showing off to others.</font>

98
00:06:57,340 --> 00:06:59,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The same could be said for my magic.</font>

99
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:04,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plenty of people have told me that 
it's unfortunate I have production magic.</font>

100
00:07:04,190 --> 00:07:07,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My father even called me a failure.</font>

101
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I've brought everyone
 happiness with this magic.</font>

102
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:16,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure they'll all enjoy
 your marionette magic, too.</font>

103
00:07:18,320 --> 00:07:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've always lived under the assumption
 that I'm worthless, but...</font>

104
00:07:24,970 --> 00:07:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you think I can do it,
Lord Van, I'll give it a try.</font>

105
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's this?</font>

106
00:07:33,380 --> 00:07:34,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's going on?</font>

107
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Did you hear anything?</font>

108
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:37,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's happening?</font>

109
00:07:37,450 --> 00:07:39,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van summoned us all here.</font>

110
00:07:39,370 --> 00:07:41,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what's going to happen.</font>

111
00:07:41,020 --> 00:07:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Are the people in the back good?</font>

112
00:07:42,620 --> 00:07:45,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}What's Lord Van going to do?</font>

113
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I can't see.</font>

114
00:07:50,900 --> 00:07:54,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, everyone, 
for gathering here today.</font>

115
00:07:54,570 --> 00:07:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We will now put on a show
 using Lady Arte's magic.</font>

116
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:01,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put on a show using magic?</font>

117
00:08:01,420 --> 00:08:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What kind of magic?</font>

118
00:08:11,590 --> 00:08:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. It's like it's alive.</font>

119
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But isn't that...</font>

120
00:08:16,270 --> 00:08:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's marionette magic, right?</font>

121
00:08:18,030 --> 00:08:22,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't someone try to take out
the royal family and nobility using that?</font>

122
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:25,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You bring me such grief!</i></font>

123
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this?</font>

124
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It stopped?</font>

125
00:08:30,710 --> 00:08:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hope she's not losing control.</font>

126
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lady Arte.</font>

127
00:08:34,660 --> 00:08:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, everyone. Don't go thinking 
the puppet's going to curtsy to you.</font>

128
00:08:39,430 --> 00:08:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The magic of vile criminals."</i></font>

129
00:08:41,960 --> 00:08:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Marionette magic often gets labeled
 as such and discriminated against.</i></font>

130
00:08:45,790 --> 00:08:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're about to see 
what Lady Arte's magic can <i>really</i> do.</font>

131
00:08:49,060 --> 00:08:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How is everyone going 
to view her after this?</i></font>

132
00:08:51,770 --> 00:08:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How will they interact with her?</i></font>

133
00:08:53,620 --> 00:08:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She must be terrified imagining all that.</i></font>

134
00:08:56,700 --> 00:08:59,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it'll be okay.</i></font>

135
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a lovely dance.</i></font>

136
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lady Arte's marionette magic 
breathes life into lifeless objects.</i></font>

137
00:09:51,270 --> 00:09:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is truly wonderful magic.</i></font>

138
00:10:38,070 --> 00:10:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bravo!</font>

139
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was a beautiful dance!</font>

140
00:10:41,130 --> 00:10:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, what incredible magic!</font>

141
00:10:42,960 --> 00:10:45,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Marionette magic is capable of that?</font>

142
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way it moved was incredible!</font>

143
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:49,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was so scared.</i></font>

144
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:50,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lady Arte, move your doll some more!</font>

145
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:52,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I always thought 
this was an awful aptitude.</i></font>

146
00:10:50,950 --> 00:10:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Your doll was beautiful!</font>

147
00:10:52,770 --> 00:10:54,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Do some more!</font>

148
00:10:54,400 --> 00:10:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I've never seen anything so beautiful!</font>

149
00:10:55,090 --> 00:10:57,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte, you did it.</font>

150
00:11:07,700 --> 00:11:11,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so, so much.</font>

151
00:11:13,390 --> 00:11:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van, urgent news!</font>

152
00:11:15,360 --> 00:11:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

153
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A carriage bearing the royal family's 
crest is heading our way.</font>

154
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The royal family?</font>

155
00:11:27,790 --> 00:11:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi, young man.</font>

156
00:11:29,380 --> 00:11:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Panamera. It's been a while.</font>

157
00:11:32,210 --> 00:11:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, that's an awfully lukewarm response.
 Did you find another woman?</font>

158
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte and I have grown much closer.</font>

159
00:11:40,970 --> 00:11:44,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while, Lady Panamera.</font>

160
00:11:45,830 --> 00:11:48,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, boy. What kind of trick did you pull?</font>

161
00:11:48,860 --> 00:11:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How has she changed so much
 in such a short time?</font>

162
00:11:52,580 --> 00:11:55,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I wonder what it could've been.</font>

163
00:11:55,410 --> 00:11:58,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Arte appeared to 
lack confidence in her magic,</font>

164
00:11:58,550 --> 00:12:01,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I just told her how wonderful it is.</font>

165
00:12:02,950 --> 00:12:07,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got some slick moves. 
Your future looks bright.</font>

166
00:12:07,970 --> 00:12:10,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoops. I got caught chatting.</font>

167
00:12:10,930 --> 00:12:14,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, bow your head, boy. 
You stand before His Majesty.</font>

168
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

169
00:12:16,950 --> 00:12:18,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? His Majesty?</i></font>

170
00:12:23,470 --> 00:12:26,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you are Van Nei Fertio?</font>

171
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Raise your head.</font>

172
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Dino En Tsora Bellrinet, 
king of Scuderia.</font>

173
00:12:34,700 --> 00:12:37,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I am his chancellor, Aperta.</font>

174
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have officially become a baron and 
joined the lower ranks of the nobility.</font>

175
00:12:42,860 --> 00:12:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must dedicate yourself 
for the benefit of our nation.</font>

176
00:12:46,530 --> 00:12:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Majesty. I humbly comply.</font>

177
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I expect great things.</font>

178
00:12:51,290 --> 00:12:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, I hear you have discovered 
a dungeon within your barony?</font>

179
00:12:56,010 --> 00:12:58,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone will be by to inquire about it,</font>

180
00:12:58,040 --> 00:13:01,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so give them a full, honest account of it.</font>

181
00:13:01,690 --> 00:13:03,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will not tolerate lies or falsehoods.</font>

182
00:13:03,800 --> 00:13:04,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, Your Majesty.</font>

183
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lastly, defeating a forest dragon 
is a truly wonderful feat.</font>

184
00:13:10,170 --> 00:13:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Given the exceptional claim 
and location this time,</font>

185
00:13:13,130 --> 00:13:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His Majesty has come 
to confirm it in person.</font>

186
00:13:16,060 --> 00:13:21,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will answer all of my questions
accurately. No objections, I presume?</font>

187
00:13:21,820 --> 00:13:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. I vow to give you 
an honest account of everything.</font>

188
00:13:25,660 --> 00:13:28,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, I'd like you 
to promise me one thing.</font>

189
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

190
00:13:29,950 --> 00:13:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can show you how everything happened,</font>

191
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:35,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but if you don't believe it all, 
it might seem like a lie to you.</font>

192
00:13:35,870 --> 00:13:38,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I ask Your Majesty
 to keep an open mind.</font>

193
00:13:39,910 --> 00:13:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're every bit as interesting 
as Viscountess Cayenne told me.</font>

194
00:13:43,730 --> 00:13:45,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can make that promise.</font>

195
00:13:46,950 --> 00:13:52,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, so the small village 
you see here is Seatoh.</font>

196
00:13:53,160 --> 00:13:58,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ramparts, gates, and moat 
are the cornerstones of its defense.</font>

197
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ballistae atop the ramparts
 are the core of its offense.</font>

198
00:14:03,780 --> 00:14:06,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aperta, what do you think?</font>

199
00:14:06,100 --> 00:14:11,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, ballistae are good for taking on
certain-sized foes at a limited distance,</font>

200
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they're quite inconvenient to use.</font>

201
00:14:14,260 --> 00:14:17,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then allow me to show you a test.</font>

202
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khamsin! Fire into the forest!</font>

203
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:21,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I go!</font>

204
00:14:28,590 --> 00:14:31,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was astounding force and distance.</font>

205
00:14:31,060 --> 00:14:33,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, it fired two bolts in succession.</font>

206
00:14:33,770 --> 00:14:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pulling off an attack like that without 
an elite archer or a mage is astonishing.</font>

207
00:14:40,350 --> 00:14:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm also curious about 
your star-shaped ramparts.</font>

208
00:14:43,730 --> 00:14:46,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, our star-shaped fortress?</font>

209
00:14:46,650 --> 00:14:53,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This shape allows us to attack enemies 
from multiple directions.</font>

210
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:56,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those bolts raining down from 
every angle would be terrifying.</font>

211
00:14:57,300 --> 00:15:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As it stands, these defenses are perfect
 against all but aerial attacks.</font>

212
00:15:01,370 --> 00:15:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aerial attacks?</font>

213
00:15:03,290 --> 00:15:09,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've made several, but I won't be
sure how well they work until I test them.</font>

214
00:15:09,380 --> 00:15:13,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You speak as if you make 
these weapons yourself, baron.</font>

215
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:15,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's because I do.</font>

216
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:19,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I seem to remember telling you 
I won't tolerate lies and falsehoods.</font>

217
00:15:19,290 --> 00:15:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swear I'm not lying.</font>

218
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, I understand your 
reservations, but please hear him out.</font>

219
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're in for even more of a shock.</font>

220
00:15:30,750 --> 00:15:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who came up with the designs 
for the ramparts?</font>

221
00:15:33,780 --> 00:15:36,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their structure seems awfully unique.</font>

222
00:15:36,530 --> 00:15:37,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

223
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:40,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the village's development?</font>

224
00:15:40,080 --> 00:15:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This scale of development
would take several years.</font>

225
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I worked really hard to build it all.</font>

226
00:15:45,410 --> 00:15:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And everyone helped out 
by gathering materials.</font>

227
00:15:48,420 --> 00:15:52,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then how many years did it take you
 to erect these ramparts?</font>

228
00:15:52,430 --> 00:15:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, roughly four months, I think?</font>

229
00:15:57,090 --> 00:15:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you understand it?</font>

230
00:15:58,790 --> 00:16:01,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I find it almost impossible to fathom.</font>

231
00:16:01,270 --> 00:16:05,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty. Perhaps it'd be best
 if he gave you a demonstration?</font>

232
00:16:05,560 --> 00:16:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine by me.</font>

233
00:16:06,910 --> 00:16:09,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's head down to the lake.</font>

234
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Lord Van!</font>

235
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Lord Van.</font>

236
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:16,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good afternoon, Lord Van.</font>

237
00:16:16,570 --> 00:16:18,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have a good day, Lord Van.</font>

238
00:16:18,600 --> 00:16:19,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, too.</font>

239
00:16:19,850 --> 00:16:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's all enjoy some meat 
together again sometime.</font>

240
00:16:22,590 --> 00:16:24,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure! We'll look forward to it!</font>

241
00:16:25,090 --> 00:16:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron, were those the villagers?</font>

242
00:16:28,460 --> 00:16:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, they were.</font>

243
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So the lord and his people can have
 such casual conversations?</font>

244
00:16:34,470 --> 00:16:37,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, uh, we can?</font>

245
00:16:51,430 --> 00:16:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Who are they?</font>

246
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:55,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's Lord Van.</font>

247
00:16:55,130 --> 00:16:57,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Howdy! Where're ya goin'?</font>

248
00:16:57,620 --> 00:17:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have some business down at the lake.</font>

249
00:17:00,280 --> 00:17:01,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all doing well?</font>

250
00:17:01,870 --> 00:17:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Course! Right, you guys?</font>

251
00:17:07,910 --> 00:17:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Glad to see you're so full
 of energy like always.</font>

252
00:17:11,130 --> 00:17:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-Baron, who were those men?</font>

253
00:17:14,630 --> 00:17:19,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're adventurers. We've bonded while 
they're here checking out the dungeon.</font>

254
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is that...</font>

255
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:33,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's my son-in-law.</font>

256
00:17:33,780 --> 00:17:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ladavesta, I'm not 
your son-in-law, remember?</font>

257
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unless my eyes deceive me, these 
are apkallu. They're incredibly rare.</font>

258
00:17:44,670 --> 00:17:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a coincidence, Your Majesty. 
That's exactly what I'm seeing.</font>

259
00:17:48,540 --> 00:17:53,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe there are apkallu 
living so out in the open here.</font>

260
00:17:53,330 --> 00:17:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen a sight like this before.</font>

261
00:17:58,400 --> 00:18:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Esparda, should we build
another tall rampart beyond the lake?</font>

262
00:18:12,990 --> 00:18:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, the finishing touches.</font>

263
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So yeah, that's how I make the walls.</font>

264
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:28,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What would you like me
 to show you next?</font>

265
00:18:33,090 --> 00:18:36,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Son-in-law, is that man another chief?</font>

266
00:18:36,170 --> 00:18:40,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, well, he's more like a great chieftain
 who coordinates many chiefs.</font>

267
00:18:40,840 --> 00:18:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh. Then I should pay him
 the utmost respect.</font>

268
00:18:45,860 --> 00:18:48,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those of us who lead tribes 
owe each other respect.</font>

269
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great chieftain.</font>

270
00:18:52,610 --> 00:18:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Ladavesta, chieftain 
of the Lada tribe.</font>

271
00:18:56,780 --> 00:19:01,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the king of this nation, 
Dino En Tsora Bellrinet.</font>

272
00:19:01,790 --> 00:19:04,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm delighted to meet you, Sir Ladavesta.</font>

273
00:19:04,870 --> 00:19:07,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed. Likewise.</font>

274
00:19:07,500 --> 00:19:10,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Allow me to present you with a gift
 as a sign of our friendship.</font>

275
00:19:11,750 --> 00:19:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way. Is that...</font>

276
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orichalcum?</font>

277
00:19:15,630 --> 00:19:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The legendary metal known 
as the "metal of the gods"?</font>

278
00:19:19,630 --> 00:19:22,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't expect to lay eyes 
on such a rare resource.</font>

279
00:19:22,010 --> 00:19:24,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we forge a sword 
with this orichalcum,</font>

280
00:19:24,210 --> 00:19:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it'd cost somewhere north 
of a hundred platinum!</font>

281
00:19:27,520 --> 00:19:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would the expense concern you?</font>

282
00:19:30,480 --> 00:19:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would be an instant national treasure.
As such, it would be priceless.</font>

283
00:19:36,540 --> 00:19:38,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup, I think it turned out well.</font>

284
00:19:38,650 --> 00:19:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is that...</font>

285
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

286
00:19:43,380 --> 00:19:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did we just see you make 
a sword from orichalcum?</font>

287
00:19:47,290 --> 00:19:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baron, I told you not to tell any lies.</font>

288
00:19:52,290 --> 00:19:54,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can make swords, can't you?</font>

289
00:19:54,540 --> 00:19:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not really sure 
what you're talking about.</font>

290
00:19:58,170 --> 00:20:01,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boy, answer honestly.</font>

291
00:20:01,170 --> 00:20:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you have any demands, 
I'll hear you out.</font>

292
00:20:03,250 --> 00:20:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise to pay what 
your honesty is worth.</font>

293
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, please grant me 
permanent residency in this village.</font>

294
00:20:11,230 --> 00:20:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter what happens, 
never send me to a different land.</font>

295
00:20:15,490 --> 00:20:16,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's all I ask.</font>

296
00:20:16,810 --> 00:20:17,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

297
00:20:17,900 --> 00:20:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you came to the capital,</font>

298
00:20:19,490 --> 00:20:22,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'd be treated well
regardless of your status.</font>

299
00:20:22,070 --> 00:20:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who would protect the people here 
if I left this land?</font>

300
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Creating a land where people
 can live in peace</font>

301
00:20:28,820 --> 00:20:32,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">without struggling to secure 
food, clothing, and shelter...</font>

302
00:20:32,060 --> 00:20:34,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the duty of a lord.</font>

303
00:20:34,130 --> 00:20:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I have an obligation 
to make this land prosper.</font>

304
00:20:42,210 --> 00:20:43,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

305
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Frankly, it's a shame 
to leave your talents out here,</font>

306
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:49,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but even if you won't come to the capital,</font>

307
00:20:49,270 --> 00:20:52,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you'll work with us if I send
 an emissary here, yes?</font>

308
00:20:53,060 --> 00:20:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, Your Majesty.</font>

309
00:20:54,840 --> 00:20:57,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it's within my power, 
I'll offer what aid I can.</font>

310
00:21:01,270 --> 00:21:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't be shocked anymore.</font>

311
00:21:03,570 --> 00:21:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've decided to stop viewing you
 as a child, baron.</font>

312
00:21:07,150 --> 00:21:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>At least I've managed to avoid 
moving to the royal capital.</i></font>

313
00:21:10,590 --> 00:21:15,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm gonna keep improving this land
 so I can lead a life of leisure.</i></font>

314
00:21:15,190 --> 00:21:17,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Hooray for the slow life.</i></font>

315
00:21:18,830 --> 00:21:24,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unfortunately, I can't afford to be away 
from the royal capital for very long.</font>

316
00:21:24,090 --> 00:21:26,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could I confirm the dungeon next?</font>

317
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:30,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The dungeon is far enough away 
that a round trip takes all day.</font>

318
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:32,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I advise against visiting it today.</font>

319
00:21:32,930 --> 00:21:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your attitude toward me is 
steadily growing more casual, isn't it?</font>

320
00:21:37,990 --> 00:21:40,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, uh, not at all!</font>

321
00:21:40,430 --> 00:21:42,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Emergency!</font>

322
00:21:42,800 --> 00:21:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Van! I-It's a dragon!</font>

323
00:21:45,740 --> 00:21:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, to the defenses!</font>

324
00:21:47,460 --> 00:21:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send word to the adventurers!</font>

325
00:21:49,070 --> 00:21:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

326
00:21:50,850 --> 00:21:52,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, boy, do you need help?</font>

327
00:21:52,850 --> 00:21:55,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, please.</font>

328
00:21:55,540 --> 00:21:56,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's the dragon?</font>

329
00:21:56,730 --> 00:21:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right there!</font>

330
00:22:16,690 --> 00:22:20,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TRANSLATION: JOHN PICKETT</font>

331
00:22:21,190 --> 00:22:25,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}TIMING: ANDY ELLIS
EDITING: SMR</font>

332
00:22:26,120 --> 00:22:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}QUALITY CONTROL: RILEY DALTON
TRANSLATION CHECK: REI MIYASAKA</font>

333
00:23:34,970 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}NEXT EPISODE: A SECRET WEAPON'S
VILLAINOUS ATTACK ON THE HOMELAND</font>

